sequenceDiagram
    autonumber

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over Client,ModelStorage: Flow 1: InferenceService Model Serving Request
        participant Client as External Client
        participant Gateway as Istio Gateway /<br/>OpenShift Router<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant VS as VirtualService /<br/>HTTPRoute
        participant OAuthProxy as oauth-proxy /<br/>kube-rbac-proxy<br/>8443/TCP
        participant Predictor as Predictor Pod<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
        participant ModelStorage as Model Storage<br/>(S3/GCS/Azure)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS

        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/{model}:predict<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
        Gateway->>VS: Forward via VirtualService/HTTPRoute<br/>HTTP/80, mTLS (Istio)
        VS->>OAuthProxy: Route to predictor service<br/>HTTP/80, mTLS (Istio)
        OAuthProxy->>Predictor: Authenticated request<br/>HTTP/8080, localhost (no TLS)
        Note over Predictor,ModelStorage: Model loaded at init time by storage-initializer
        Predictor-->>OAuthProxy: Prediction response (JSON)
        OAuthProxy-->>VS: Response
        VS-->>Gateway: Response
        Gateway-->>Client: HTTPS response<br/>TLS 1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(255, 248, 240)
        Note over Client,DecodePod: Flow 2: LLMInferenceService (Disaggregated Prefill/Decode)
        participant GW2 as Gateway<br/>(HTTPRoute)<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant Scheduler as InferencePool<br/>Scheduler<br/>gRPC TLS
        participant PrefillPod as Prefill Pod<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS
        participant DecodePod as Decode Pod<br/>(via routing sidecar)<br/>8000/TCP HTTPS

        Client->>GW2: POST inference request<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        GW2->>Scheduler: Forward to InferencePool<br/>gRPC, TLS
        Scheduler->>PrefillPod: Route to prefill workload<br/>HTTPS/8000, TLS (self-signed)
        PrefillPod->>DecodePod: KV cache transfer via routing sidecar<br/>HTTPS/8000, TLS (self-signed)
        DecodePod-->>GW2: Streaming response
        GW2-->>Client: HTTPS response<br/>TLS 1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over LMCacheCR,NodePV: Flow 3: LocalModel Cache Download
        participant LMCacheCR as LocalModelCache CR
        participant LMCtrl as localmodel-controller
        participant LMNodeAgent as localmodelnode-agent
        participant DownloadJob as Download Job<br/>(storage-initializer)
        participant CloudStorage as Cloud Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
        participant NodePV as Node Local PV<br/>(Filesystem)

        LMCacheCR->>LMCtrl: CRD Watch event
        LMCtrl->>LMCtrl: Create PV/PVC<br/>K8s API HTTPS/6443
        LMCtrl->>LMCtrl: Update LocalModelNode spec<br/>K8s API HTTPS/6443
        LMNodeAgent->>LMNodeAgent: Watch LocalModelNode changes
        LMNodeAgent->>DownloadJob: Create download Job<br/>K8s API HTTPS/6443
        DownloadJob->>CloudStorage: Download model artifacts<br/>HTTPS/443, TLS 1.2+<br/>Auth: Storage credentials
        CloudStorage-->>DownloadJob: Model artifacts
        DownloadJob->>NodePV: Write to local PV<br/>Filesystem I/O
    end

    rect rgb(248, 240, 255)
        Note over IGClient,ISvcB: Flow 4: InferenceGraph DAG Routing
        participant IGClient as Client
        participant IGRouter as kserve-router<br/>8080/TCP HTTP/HTTPS
        participant TokenReview as K8s TokenReview API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS
        participant ISvcA as InferenceService A<br/>80/TCP HTTP
        participant ISvcB as InferenceService B<br/>80/TCP HTTP

        IGClient->>IGRouter: POST inference request<br/>HTTP(S)/8080, TLS (optional)<br/>Auth: Bearer Token (optional)
        IGRouter->>TokenReview: Validate bearer token<br/>HTTPS/6443, ServiceAccount Token
        TokenReview-->>IGRouter: Token valid
        IGRouter->>ISvcA: Fan-out: Step 1 (splitter/ensemble)<br/>HTTP/80, mTLS (mesh)
        ISvcA-->>IGRouter: Partial result
        IGRouter->>ISvcB: Fan-out: Step 2 (switch/sequence)<br/>HTTP/80, mTLS (mesh)
        ISvcB-->>IGRouter: Partial result
        IGRouter->>IGRouter: Aggregate results (ensemble/sequence)
        IGRouter-->>IGClient: Combined response<br/>HTTP(S)/8080
    end
